{"tid":1878984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奴工署：員工被強制檢疫（但無確診）唔當病假，要扣大假","createTime":"2020-02-14T02:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T06:04:47.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4445f09cab3341e9bb3b2138f5816b8fd697db","tid":1878984,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:25:17.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】強制檢疫14天冇確診不獲病假！勞工處僅籲僱主彈性處理「缺勤」<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續擴大，勞工處因應疫情近日發出一份新指引文件，解釋僱主和僱員在《僱傭條例》下的責任及權利。<span style=\"color: red;\">該份由勞工處勞資關係科發出的文件中，明確表明即使僱員被要求強制檢疫而缺勤，僱員需要染病才可獲得病假；至於僱員沒有染病，政府只「鼓勵」僱主彈性處理，以在家工作或視作放取有薪假代替。</span>職工盟主席吳敏兒批評，強制檢疫非僱員所樂見，若僱主扣大假或扣薪，對員工絕不公平，她亦擔心勞工處的指引不清晰，會徒添勞資爭拗。<br />\n<br />\n全文link：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200213/FWTQJPUPY3A65QLVX4X56CCXRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FFWTQJPUPY3A65QLVX4X56CCXRI%2F&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvU9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=196770fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200213%2FFWTQJPUPY3A65QLVX4X56CCXRI%2F&h=92130cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200213/FWTQJPUPY3A65QLVX4X56CCXRI/</a>"},{"pid":"9a19b58b14eb5d8e0234ef9aaa008973ac5ffb11","tid":1878984,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4511bea0b480348a849a32821ac01482e001f5ea","tid":1878984,"uid":135409,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:28:20.000Z","msg":"呢個政府有無做過任何好事?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847b451152f9ac5c5216f0df730ff977c4ea91d4","tid":1878984,"uid":60000,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T02:29:37.000Z",